last_episode_to_air.overview: Alexa is on the wrong side of a murder investigation, fighting to clear her own name while avoiding the webs of the three Black Widows.

name: My Life Is Murder
overview: Investigator Alexa Crowe, cannot help fighting the good fight – whether it is solving murders or combatting the small frustrations of everyday life. Fearless and unapologetic, Alexa's unique skills and insights into the darker quirks of human nature, allows her to provoke, comfort and push the right buttons as she unravels the truth behind the most baffling of crimes.

episodes.name: The Boyfriend Experience
episodes.overview: Former detective Alexa Crowe is lured into the world of murder and mystery when her friend and colleague asks her to look into the death of a woman who fell from the balcony of a male escort.

episodes.name: The Locked Room
episodes.overview: A man is found shot dead in a motel room. The door has been chain-locked from the inside. Someone killed him and escaped when the door was locked from the inside.

episodes.name: Lividity in Lycra
episodes.overview: Cycling groups are the ultimate opportunity for networking and power broking. But when the CFO of a hospitality empire dies on his morning ride, Alexa must infiltrate the world of lycra and butt pads.

episodes.name: Can't Stand the Heat
episodes.overview: Alexa is thrown into the world of culinary excellence while investigating the death of a cooking school student. Alexa must hone her chops to uncover a tangled web of lies, rivalry and secrets.

episodes.name: Feet of Clay
episodes.overview: Alexa investigates the hit and run death of a young woman. Although the drunk driver involved turned herself in, Alexa believes the accident may be the work of an opportunistic killer.

episodes.name: Another Bloody Podcast
episodes.overview: Alexa investigates a case that runs the gamut of birth, marriage and murder when a young man is found dead in an alley after a fight at his brothers wedding.

episodes.name: Old School
episodes.overview: Alexa's past catches up to her as she returns to her exclusive, private high school to investigate the mysterious death of her much beloved former teacher.

episodes.name: Remains to Be Seen
episodes.overview: After a near-death experience, Alexa is confronted by her own mortality as she explores the „Big Death” industry to unravel the secrets of a murdered man whose body was found in someone elses grave.

episodes.name: Fake Empire
episodes.overview: When a clairvoyant contacts the police about a murder, offering details that have never been released to the public, Alexa jumps at the opportunity to prove that clairvoyants are frauds.

episodes.name: Mirror Mirror
episodes.overview: When a cosmetic surgeon dies after self-administering an anti-wrinkle drug, Alexa immerses herself the world of the beautiful and the vain to uncover what really happened to the bright young doctor.

episodes.name: Call of the Wild
episodes.overview: When a woman shoots a stranger at point blank range by Auckland Harbour, it looks like an open-and-shut case. But investigator Alexa Crowe discovers not everything is as it seems.

episodes.name: Oceans Apart
episodes.overview: Alexa's investigation into the death of a surfing champion takes her back to an old childhood haunt. But what is the victim's influencer girlfriend trying to hide? And why is Alexa so reluctant to spend time at one of the world's best beaches?

episodes.name: All That Glitters
episodes.overview: Alexa's personal and professional lives collide when she investigates the death of a drag queen whose career was on the rise.

episodes.name: Look Don't Touch
episodes.overview: Alexa is confronted by her own history when she investigates the death of a museum curator.

episodes.name: Crushed Dreams
episodes.overview: Alexa will need all five senses to solve the mysterious death of an ambitious young winemaker.

episodes.name: Sleep No More
episodes.overview: A frosty reception awaits Alexa when she investigates how the chef at a resort died in his own walk-in freezer.

episodes.name: All The Better To See You
episodes.overview: All the worlds a stage when Alexa investigates a murder of an actor in the middle of a live performance.

episodes.name: Hidden Gems
episodes.overview: Alexa must sort fact from fiction when a compulsive liar confesses to a murder at a high-end jeweler.

episodes.name: Wild Life
episodes.overview: Harry asks Alexa to look into the case of his friend accused of murdering a survival expert.

episodes.name: Pleasure and Pain
episodes.overview: Alexa investigates the death of a self-help guru and ends up in a cat-and-mouse game with the victim's mysterious wife.

episodes.name: It Takes Two
episodes.overview: When Alexa investigates the death of a young teacher at a tango club, it's not clear who is leading whom in a dangerous dance to discover the truth.

episodes.name: Nothing Concrete
episodes.overview: Truth is stranger than fiction when a crime novelist is found dead, encased in a public sculpture. Alexa uncovers a plot more deadly than any of the victim's novels.

episodes.name: Bloodlines
episodes.overview: Alexa is determined to prove the innocence of a champion thoroughbred blamed for the death of his handler at a successful horse breeding stud, where secrets lurk and blood is thicker than water.

episodes.name: The Village
episodes.overview: Alexa investigates a death at an upscale retirement village where a quiet life is the last thing residents want, and where her brother's involvement with the victims feels too close to home.

episodes.name: Silent Lights
episodes.overview: When Christmas lights aficionado Paddy falls from his roof, Alexa finds herself untangling a mystery as tangled as Paddy's beloved lights.

episodes.name: Bride To Bee
episodes.overview: When a bride dies from an allergic reaction to a bee sting on her wedding day, Alexa must discover whether this is just a tragic accident... or a case where revenge is as sweet as honey.

episodes.name: Breaking Bread
episodes.overview: Feuding celebrity bakers put Alexa through her paces when a man is found drowned with a rare flour in his lungs.

episodes.name: Gaslight Sonata
episodes.overview: Alexa and Madison's investigation into the death of a music producer is complicated by the arrival of a young girl at Alexa's door with some very big news.

episodes.name: Staying Mum
episodes.overview: When Alexa investigates the death of a popular male nanny, she discovers some pushy parents are more terrifying than most killers she has met before.

episodes.name: Rising Angel
episodes.overview: Alexa investigates a young model’s death backstage at a fashion show.

episodes.name: To Dye For
episodes.overview: A wealthy socialite dies in suspicious circumstances, leaving her entire fortune to her cat. To uncover the truth, Alexa investigates a heady world of high society gossip.

episodes.name: Tough Love
episodes.overview: Alexa’s investigates the death of a tough tennis coach, but she’s not the only one on the case. A glamorous private investigator is determined to solve the case before Alexa.

episodes.name: Location, Location, Location
episodes.overview: A real estate agent is found dead at an open home, and Alexa’s investigation takes a supernatural turn when the homeowner insists the 100 year old house is cursed.

episodes.name: One Man’s Poison
episodes.overview: Alexa investigates ‘death by stir-fry’ when Reuben is desperate for her to clear the name of his friend, a private chef accused of poisoning one of this clients.

episodes.name: En Pointe
episodes.overview: A ballerina has been shot dead with a bow and arrow at a prestigious ballet academy. While Madison tries her hand at archery, Alexa poses as a dance mom to uncover the terrible truth.

episodes.name: The Good Oil
episodes.overview: Alexa ignores her own family problems to find justice for grieving Samoan matriarch Eme, whose son Ropati was shot dead at a botched robbery at his coconut oil factory.

episodes.name: The Widow’s Club (1)
episodes.overview: Alexa and her brother Will infiltrate an exclusive country club, where a group of wealthy golf widows have the men running scared.

episodes.name: The Widow’s Club (2)
episodes.overview: Alexa is on the wrong side of a murder investigation, fighting to clear her own name while avoiding the webs of the three Black Widows.
